data.description: Location, location, location! Looking for a move-in ready home in a suburb area? If so, this is the one for you! This turn-key home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 1476 sq ft, vaulted ceilings, spacious kitchen, attached 2 car garage, wood-burning fireplace, large 0.15 acre lot, and much more! Home has just been professionally cleaned with new carpet installed in the bedrooms as well! Covered porch area in the backyard is perfect for entertainment.  Additionally, the furnace, AC unit, & hot water heater were replaced in 2019 to alleviate all your heating/cooling concerns. Truly can't go wrong with this one, so contact your agent today for a personal tour, before it's too late!
